Managing cardiovascular risk in people living with HIV in Asia - where are we 
now?

Choi JY(1)(2), Lui GCY(3), Liao CT(4)(5)(6), Yang CJ(7)(8).

Author information:
(1)Division of Infectious Diseases, Department of Internal Medicine, Yonsei 
University College of Medicine, Seoul, South Korea.
