Resistance and aerobic exercise intervention during chemotherapy in patients 
with metastatic cancer: a pilot study in South Korea.

Park JH(1), Park KD(2), Kim JH(3), Kim YS(1), Kim EY(4), Ahn HK(1), Park I(1), 
Sym SJ(1).

Author information:
(1)Division of Medical Oncology, Department of Internal Medicine, Gil Medical 
Center, Gachon University College of Medicine, Incheon, South Korea.
(2)Department of Rehabilitation Medicine, Gil Medical Center, Gachon University 
College of Medicine, Incheon, South Korea.
(3)Clinical Rehabilitation Research Center, Korea Worker's Compensation & 
